data.description: Enjoy Resort style living in the award-winning community of Riverfront. This beautiful end unit townhouse condo offers 4BR & 3 1/2 BA. The primary bedroom with an en-suite bath and walk-in closet is located on the main floor. The family room with a gas fireplace, high ceilings and a wall of windows looking out to the golf course is great for entertaining. The open kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, new backsplash and a breakfast bar. There is a large screened porch & deck ready for you to enjoy your morning coffee. The third floor has a bedroom and massive open space that can serve many purposes. On the 1st floor you will find 2 BR & 1 BA, a private patio, and a two-car garage. Brand new Trane HVAC. You will have access to two pools, two piers, the golf course, walking trails & tennis courts.  Conveniently located near I-664, Harbour View Marketplace, various restaurants, shopping, entertainment. medical facilities and much more!
